caption: There's real glory in witnessing the success emerge from your dreams, and owners Katrina Kelly and Shari Griffith are living embodiments of this truth.  The fragrant aroma of moist wings smothered in bold mesquite textures immediately hit you once inside, but it's the decorative bite-sized cakes which stole our hearts.  Cake N Wings is well-liked and the friendly atmosphere genuinely displays why Foxhurst is becoming home to the new "mom & pop shop" where customers and proprietors speak on a first name basis.  It's one of the reasons why Jazzy Underground visionary Troy Luqman Ali has spent countless hours preparing for a stellar launch in the local area.  Thanks to Katrina & Shari's passionate ingenuity, we at Jazzy Underground can't wait to host collaborative pairings with a widely respected name among local sweet eats!
